<casebody firstpage="13" lastpage="13" xmlns="http://nrs.harvard.edu/urn-3:HLS.Libr.US_Case_Law.Schema.Case_Body:v1">
<parties id="p-1">
  In the Matter of Robert A. SCHACHTER.
 </parties>
<docketnumber id="p-2">
  No. D-2828.
 </docketnumber>
<court id="p-3">
  Supreme Court of the United States
 </court>
<decisiondate id="p-4">
  July 20, 2015.
 </decisiondate>
<opinion id="p-5">
  Robert A. Schachter, of Valley Cottage, New York, having requested as a member of the Bar of this Court, it is ordered that his name be stricken from the roll of attorneys admitted to the practice of law before this Court. The Rule to Show Cause, issued on June 29, 2015, is discharged.
 </opinion>
</casebody>
